author: newsr.in
title: Colas adds fizz to D'Assisi's season with Ahmed Sailor title
text:
St Francis D'Assisi (Borivli) clinched the boys' U-16 Ahmed Sailor knockout title of the Mumbai Schools Sports Association (MSSA) inter-school football title beating Campion (Colaba) by a solitary goal at Cooperage yesterday.
